{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUserId:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString","text":"NSString"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"text":"userId","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"completion:"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":" (^"},{"text":")(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSError","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSError"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"error"},{"text":")) ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"completion"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The custom user identifier (e.g., database ID, UUID, username).","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"userId"},{"name":"completion","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Block called when the operation completes."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Receives nil on success, or an NSError on failure."}]}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Same as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"setUserId:"},{"type":"text","text":" but provides callback when the server operation completes."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Use this when you need to ensure the user ID is set before performing"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"dependent operations like merging user data or tracking critical events.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Example","level":2,"anchor":"Example"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Handle login with guaranteed user ID synchronization:"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["class LoginCoordinator {","","    func performLogin(credentials: Credentials,","                      completion: @escaping (Result<User, Error>) -> Void) {","","        APIClient.shared.login(credentials) { result in","            switch result {","            case .success(let user):","                \/\/ Set user ID with confirmation before proceeding","                Pushwoosh.configure.setUserId(user.id) { error in","                    if let error = error {","                        Logger.warning(\"User ID sync failed: \\(error.localizedDescription)\")","                        \/\/ Continue anyway - local state is still valid","                    }","","                    \/\/ Now safe to track login event with correct user attribution","                    Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","                        \"logged_in\": true,","                        \"last_login\": ISO8601DateFormatter().string(from: Date()),","                        \"login_method\": credentials.method.rawValue","                    ])","","                    \/\/ Set email if available","                    if let email = user.email {","                        Pushwoosh.configure.setEmail(email)","                    }","","                    completion(.success(user))","                }","","            case .failure(let error):","                completion(.failure(error))","            }","        }","    }","}"]}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setUserId:completion:"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets a custom user identifier with completion confirmation."}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setuserid:completion:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","role":"symbol","title":"setUserId:completion:","roleHeading":"Type Method","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setUserId:completion:","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUserId:completion:"}],"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setUserId:completion:"},"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/setUserId:completion:":{"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setuserid:completion:","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets a custom user identifier with completion confirmation."}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setUserId:completion:","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUserId:completion:"}],"type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setUserId:completion:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"setUserId:completion:"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","title":"PWConfiguration","fragments":[{"text":"PWConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","type":"topic","title":"PushwooshCore","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore"}}}